\"data\";s:1936:\"<p>As a follow up to &#8220;<a href=\"http://www.jonbishop.com/2011/06/which-bookmarking-sharing-buttons-should-i-display-on-my-site/\">Which Bookmarking &#038; Sharing Buttons Should I Display On My Site</a>&#8220;, I wanted to talk a bit about how to make those buttons display faster and how to measure their effectiveness. This is my first blog post at my new job and I wanted to share it with my readers here.</p>\n<p><strong>Read <a href=\"http://www.ampagency.com/getting-the-most-out-of-your-sharing-buttons/\" title=\"How To Make Social Sharing Buttons Display Faster and Measure Their Effectiveness\">Getting The Most Out Of Your Sharing Buttons</a> now.</strong></p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/JonBishop?a=s6LvkKPVbgo:EzMJUkxNi0Q:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/JonBishop?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/JonBishop?a=s6LvkKPVbgo:EzMJUkxNi0Q:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/JonBishop?i=s6LvkKPVbgo:EzMJUkxNi0Q:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/JonBishop?a=s6LvkKPVbgo:EzMJUkxNi0Q:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/JonBishop?i=s6LvkKPVbgo:EzMJUkxNi0Q:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/JonBishop?a=s6LvkKPVbgo:EzMJUkxNi0Q:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/JonBishop?i=s6LvkKPVbgo:EzMJUkxNi0Q:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/JonBishop?a=s6LvkKPVbgo:EzMJUkxNi0Q:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/JonBishop?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/JonBishop?a=s6LvkKPVbgo:EzMJUkxNi0Q:LQx-feW9hR8\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/JonBishop?d=LQx-feW9hR8\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/JonBishop/~4/s6LvkKPVbgo\" height=\"1\" width